<h1>Donating to Type2.com</h1>
Since 1996, Type2.com has been kept alive by the generous donations of
mailing list subscribers.  In spring 2001, both lists responded wonderfully
to a request for funds for purchasing the server we are now running on
and for paying several months' worth of our Internet connection charges.
We still have enough funds to cover the next few months, but we always
gladly accept additional donations.
<p>
If you'd like to send a check, make it payable to "Type2 Fundraiser"
and mail it to our treasurer, Ted Finesman:<br>
Ted Finesman<br>
8405 Reading Road<br>
Cincinnati OH 45215 USA
<p>
Ted has also set up a PayPal account.  Use account <b>tedebare@type2.com</b> ,
or click below.
